These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-1::.
There 2 different types of food: corn, broccoli
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating broccoli and the person who's sport is surfing have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |
| Food    | broccoli | corn  |
| Sport   | surfing    | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola
There 2 different types of food: kale, apricot
1. the person drinking mirinda and the person eating kale have the same parity positions##9
2. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |     2     |
| Beverage   | cola      | mirinda       |
| Food       | apricot | kale |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, disco
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, snowboarding
1. the fan pop and the person who's sport is parkour have different parity positions##9
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | pop       |
| Sport         | parkour | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, german
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
2. the german and the person who's sport is handball have different parity positions##9
3. the japanese is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Nationality   | german | japanese |
| Sport         | rugby | handball  |

 #################################

 
