.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-6::.
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, strawberry
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
1. the owner of the chinchilla and the person eating strawberry have the same parity positions##9
2. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |   2    |
| Food   | strawberry | lettuce  |
| Pet    | chinchilla       | horse |

